### [choco://intel-network-drivers-win10](choco://intel-network-drivers-win10/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)

---


## Introduction

This release includes software and drivers for Intel(R) Ethernet adapters and integrated network connections.

## Overview

The Microsoft Windows* download package has been split into a driver package and an Intel® PROSet package.  The driver package must be installed prior to installing the Intel® PROSet package. 
 

